              legal_reasoning: 'A dangerously competent alternative argument. The CCD remedy is genuinely powerful. But it treats the symptom, not the disease. If only the loans are voided, CrediCatch can redesign the product while keeping the exploitative AI targeting engine active. The AI Act prohibition demands the system itself be destroyed, regardless of loan terms.'
