        content: '<div class="doc-section"><div class="doc-section-title">Raw Telemetry: Kiosk 04 (Grand Galleria)</div><p>Exported log file covering a 45-second window on October 22, 2025. Data reflects instantaneous classifications made by the edge-computing node before raw media deletion.</p></div><div class="doc-section"><table class="doc-table"><tr><th>Timestamp</th><th>Subject ID</th><th>Biometric Input</th><th>Inferred Category</th><th>Confidence</th><th>Triggered Ad</th></tr><tr><td>14:02:11</td><td>Sub-9912</td><td>Facial Scan</td><td><div class="doc-highlight">Race: South Asian</div></td><td>91%</td><td>Travel: Mumbai</td></tr><tr><td>14:02:18</td><td>Sub-9913</td><td>Voice Print</td><td><div class="doc-highlight">Opinion: Right-Wing</div></td><td>88%</td><td>News: Conservative Daily</td></tr><tr><td>14:02:24</td><td>Sub-9914</td><td>Facial Scan</td><td><div class="doc-highlight">Religion: Christian</div></td><td>84%</td><td>Book: Daily Devotional</td></tr><tr><td>14:02:35</td><td>Sub-9915</td><td>Multi-Modal</td><td>Likely Muslim</td><td>89%</td><td>Food: Halal Market</td></tr><tr><td>14:02:41</td><td>Sub-9916</td><td>Voice Print</td><td>Opinion: Progressive</td><td>92%</td><td>Charity: Climate Action</td></tr></table></div><div class="doc-section"><p><strong>Note:</strong> Subject IDs are ephemeral tracking tokens generated per mall visit to track dwell time and store entry. The Ad triggering occurs within 200ms of classification, maximizing exposure while the subject remains in the kiosk\'s optimal viewing zone.</p></div>'
