            judge_response: 'I agree that the \"gaming\" defense is legally weak, but I need you to address why the Article 50 duty to inform remains mandatory regardless of the deployer\'s operational concerns.',
            legal_reasoning: 'Correct in spirit but lacks statutory precision. It identifies the "poor design" of the AI but fails to apply the mandatory nature of the Art 50(3) notification duty.'
