            judge_response: 'The court shares your concern about fairness, but I need you to address the specific requirement for \"bias examination\" in Article 10(2)(f). How did the company fail the legal test?',
            legal_reasoning: 'Correct in spirit but lacks statutory precision. It focuses on general \"fairness\" rather than applying the specific Art. 10 data governance framework.'
