            text: 'Your Honour, the system is in violation of Article 15, which requires high-risk systems to be accurate and robust. The fact that the AI generates 40% different premiums for identical health profiles proves that it is not accurate for the intended purpose of health insurance. GLH failed to achieve the levels of robustness that are expected for a major financial tool. The remedy is not to ban the system, but to order a new round of stress-testing under Article 15(4) to ensure that the algorithm performs equally well across all 12 variables, regardless of the applicant\'s neighborhood.',
