            judge_response: 'Counsel, there is no such clause in the DSA, and high-risk insurance systems are explicitly governed by the AI Act. Your jurisdictional argument is entirely false.',
            legal_reasoning: 'Fundamental error. It invents a non-existent exemption and wrongly claims the AI Act doesn\'t apply to insurance companies.'
