            judge_response: 'Counsel, you are conflating two different duties. Article 13 transparency is for the *deployer* to understand the system. Is the voter a \"user\" in the sense of Article 13, or is the voter a \"natural person\" protected by the disclosure rules of Article 50?',
            legal_reasoning: 'This is the trap. It misapplies Article 13 (which is about the deployer\'s understanding of the system) to the public disclosure duty (which is Article 50). It also wrongly classifies the voter as the "user" under Article 13.'
