            legal_reasoning: 'This is the trap. It misclassifies a transparency breach as a "Prohibited Practice" (Art 5). While manipulative, a chatbot pretending to be human is specifically addressed by the disclosure rules of Art 50, not the high-threshold "subliminal manipulation" ban.'
