            judge_response: 'Counsel, the Authority appreciates the concern for your client, but fairness as a general sentiment does not constitute a legal argument. You must identify the specific provision of GDPR that HealthGuard has infringed and explain how the facts satisfy its conditions. Please reframe your submission.',
            legal_reasoning: 'Fails to cite Art. 22(1) or any GDPR provision. Makes no legal argument about "solely automated" or "legal effects." Relies entirely on intuitive unfairness, which carries no weight before a supervisory authority conducting a legal analysis.'
