            judge_response: 'Counsel, you gesture toward valid concerns but do not ground them in the specific legal requirements of Art. 22(2)(c) or Art. 7. The Authority requires a precise legal argument identifying what the provision demands and how HealthGuard failed to meet it. Please be more specific.',
            legal_reasoning: 'Correctly identifies the consent problem intuitively but cites no articles. Does not distinguish between consent to data sharing and consent to automated decision-making. Does not engage with the legal standard in Art. 22(2)(c) for what "explicit consent" means in this context.'
