      title: 'Witness Statement \u2014 Regional Manager Ana Carvalho',
      date: '2025-03-11',
      content: '<div class="doc-section"><p class="doc-section-title">Witness Statement of Ana Carvalho, Regional Manager, QuickFleet Logistics Lda</p><p>I am the line manager who confirmed Paulo Silva\'s termination on 22 January 2025. I want to be clear about what that confirmation involved in practice.</p><p>On that shift I had 38 files to process. Each file appeared on my screen as a driver name, a composite score, and a flag reason \u2014 in Mr. Silva\'s case, \u201Cbelow-threshold efficiency, three consecutive periods.\u201D <span class="doc-highlight">I had no access to HR records, route assignment documentation, or approved handling protocols from the DriverScore interface.</span> To check those systems I would need to log into a separate HR portal, search by employee ID, and navigate to the correct folder. That process takes five to ten minutes per file.</p><p><span class="doc-highlight">With 38 files to process in a shift, I physically cannot open the HR system for every driver. I spent approximately 14 seconds on Mr. Silva\'s file. I did not know he was on a medical route. I was not provided that information. I clicked confirm.</span> I raised concerns about the KPI target in November 2024. I received no response.</p></div>'
