    context: 'You are cross-examining Ricardo Fonseca, who designed the termination review KPI and authorised the DriverScore confirmation workflow. He will defend the 40-per-shift target as operationally necessary and argue that a human manager confirming every decision constitutes adequate review under GDPR.',
