                'Art. 22(1) applies where a decision is based solely on automated processing producing legal effects or similarly significantly affecting the data subject. A priority score determining wait time in a stroke emergency significantly affects the patient. The architecture confirms nurses cannot adjust the score. Processing health data for this decision engages Art. 9(1) \u2014 use ev2 to establish both dimensions.'
