          category: 'effective',
          witnessResponse: 'Personalised pricing is a standard commercial practice used across the e-commerce industry. Every retailer adjusts prices based on market conditions. Our users are free to shop elsewhere. The price we show is the price we offer \u2014 users choose whether to accept it.',
