          impactExplanation: 'Forces Visser to defend the \u201Cno legal effects\u201D argument against the EDPB\'s significant financial impact standard. The follow-up extracts the admission that the company has made a legal judgment about Art. 22\'s threshold without obtaining a legal opinion, which the internal email confirms.'
