          questionText: 'Your product manager Lena Fischer wrote to you on 8 May 2024 flagging that the privacy notice does not cover personalised pricing and asking whether you should loop in legal. Your response was: \u201CPesonalised pricing is industry standard. Legal will say the same. Don\'t slow down the Q3 rollout.\u201D Did you obtain a legal opinion on whether PriceMind\'s personalised pricing requires disclosure under GDPR Art. 13 before the Q3 rollout?',
