                'Art. 22(1) applies to decisions that produce legal effects or \u201Csimilarly significantly affect\u201D the data subject. The EDPB guidelines confirm that significant financial impact on economic interests qualifies. Losing \u20AC3,000/month in income overnight is a significant financial effect. BrandGuard assigns a BSS and automatically demonetises with no human review \u2014 use ev2 to prove the solely automated element.'
