          witnessResponse: '"KidZone offers a uniquely compelling social experience. Higher engagement reflects the quality and relevance of what we offer to this age group — teenagers choose KidZone over alternatives because they find it more valuable. Comparing to industry benchmarks assumes all teen platforms offer equivalent value. Our engagement figures reflect user preference, not manipulation."',
          followUpImpact: 'negative'
