            judge_response: 'Counsel, document length is not a legal standard and "obviously inadequate" is not a legal analysis. You must apply Art. 34(1)\'s diligent assessment standard and Art. 34(2)\'s mandatory factors to explain specifically what the assessment fails to do — not simply characterise it as inadequate.',
