          feedback: 'Correct. Art. 16(1) DSA requires hosting services to put in place notice mechanisms that are easy to access and user-friendly. Art. 16(5) requires confirmation of receipt and redress information without undue delay. These specific procedural requirements were introduced by the DSA and are the directly applicable standard — replacing the ECD\'s notice-and-takedown framework with specific user-protective obligations.'
