      content: '<div class="doc-section"><div class="doc-section-title">Market Impact Statement</div><p>I represent 12,000 marketplace sellers across Europe. Since 2026, we have observed a systematic pattern where MegaMart identifies high-margin product categories through third-party seller data, then launches private-label competitors with algorithmic advantages.</p><p>Sellers report that once MegaMart enters a category, their organic visibility drops 60-80% despite maintaining perfect seller metrics. MegaMart\'s private-label products appear with "Recommended" badges within 48 hours of launch, while established sellers with years of positive reviews are relegated to page 2.</p><p>This is not market competition — it is platform capture. Sellers cannot compete with a +35% algorithmic head start.</p></div>'
