            judge_response: 'Counsel has identified the wrong regulation. This case concerns Art. 6(4) of the Digital Markets Act, which governs market access obligations for designated gatekeepers. The Digital Services Act addresses content moderation by intermediary services — a different legal instrument with different scope and remedies. Please address the DMA.',
