            judge_response: 'Counsel has described the harm correctly but has not cited the specific DMA article violated or explained why the \'integrated product\' defence fails as a matter of law. Which provision of the DMA prohibits this conduct, and does that provision contain any exception for integrated products?',
            legal_reasoning: 'Does not cite Art. 5(8) or its per se nature. No engagement with why the integration defence fails on the text of Art. 5(8). The remedy requested is correct but cannot be ordered without a finding tied to a specific legal obligation.'
