          questionText: 'Your board presentation was dated August 2024 — that is over 18 months after OmniTech\'s DMA designation obligations became effective in May 2023. Can you explain what engineering work was conducted on consent implementation during those 18 months?',
          witnessResponse: 'I would need to refer to our engineering roadmap documentation for the specific timeline of work conducted.',
          followUpImpact: 'positive'
